_:N5abc5fc0a89247fc953edf2e4dbd694f <http://schema.org/description> "The Agriculture and Horticulture Development Board (AHDB) helps to make Great Britain’s livestock, dairy and agriculture sectors more successful, providing market information to improve supply chain transparency and stimulating demand in the UK and export markets. AHDB is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ." .
